column16: Alex Rodriguez grounds into a force out, second baseman Kelly Johnson to third baseman Brett Lawrie.    Derek Jeter scores.    Curtis Granderson out at 3rd.    Mark Teixeira to 2nd.    Alex Rodriguez to 1st.
Mark Teixeira walks.    Curtis Granderson to 2nd.
Curtis Granderson singles on a ground ball to left fielder Rajai Davis.    Derek Jeter to 3rd.
Derek Jeter doubles (18) on a line drive to right fielder Anthony Gose.    Chris Stewart scores.
Chris Stewart doubles (4) on a ground ball to left fielder Rajai Davis.    Jayson Nix scores.  Chris Stewart advances to 3rd, on throwing error by left fielder Rajai Davis.
Jayson Nix singles on a ground ball to center fielder Colby Rasmus.
